  "body": "[<Center>![PMC](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/e556f05801baf51f64eb079db94542fd6cd7acd8.png)](https://www.planetminecraft.com/member/svrve/) | [![CurseForge](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/186466038ea8fdc8a1e106328e1469b76d340fd7.png)](https://www.curseforge.com/members/svrve/projects) | [![Modrinth](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/d639cdb1abcfbf97e4e313512a39293a0b55f3c8.png)](https://modrinth.com/user/Svrve) | [![Discord](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/045c08f0228147ad2f1ce76cbc4be4d1e782e798.png)](https://discord.com/)\n\n\n[<Center>![EarlyAcces](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/ccd82ceb15cb98213e7e9ef49d36ecd3bfd15871.png)](https://ko-fi.com/svrve)\n\n<Center> You can buy monthy subscription to get faster updates on KO-FI\n\n\n****\n\n# <Center> **About**\n\nThis pack is all about torches, make them an item texture, animate it, change model, also animate it. Thats all.\n\n.<Center>![Torches](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/6d8aeac3cffbb4b4a346017faa810d113c203bd4.png)\n\n\n# <Center> **FAQ**\n> **How to install resourcepacks?**\nThere are a lot of tutorial out there on youtube, that will explain this better than me, but just download something from trusted sites like modrinth or curseforge, then drag this file to folder that will pop out if you click \"Open Pack Folder\" in Minecraft.     \n\n> **Can i use some resources from it in my pack?**\nAfter installing it, open the file you downloaded (.zip). Here you will find licence. Read it.\n",
